profile: A 65 year old person, living in a living_alone family with 1_person members. The person has 2 vehicles and an annual income of 261921 dollars.
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)
        WHERE (p.age>60) OR (p.income>=120000)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Recreation'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT i) AS intention,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r1) AS want_to,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to

        WHERE (p.age>60) OR (p.income>=0 AND p.income<30000)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Recreation'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT i) AS intention,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r1) AS want_to,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to

        WHERE (p.age>60) OR (p.income>=30000 AND p.income<60000)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Recreation'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire,

            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to

profile: A 62 year old person, living in a married_couple family with 2_person members. The person has 1 vehicles and an annual income of 0 dollars.
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)
        WHERE (p.age>60) OR (p.income<0)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Recreation'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT i) AS intention,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r1) AS want_to,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to

profile: A 27 year old person, living in a nonfamily_single family with 2_person members. The person has 1 vehicles and an annual income of 82762 dollars.
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)
        WHERE (p.age>=18 AND p.age<30) OR (p.income>=60000 AND p.income<90000)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Recreation'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT i) AS intention,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r1) AS want_to,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to

profile: A 23 year old person, living in a nonfamily_single family with 3_person members. The person has 3_plus vehicles and an annual income of 51862 dollars.
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)
        WHERE (p.age>=18 AND p.age<30) OR (p.income>=30000 AND p.income<60000)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Recreation'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT i) AS intention,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r1) AS want_to,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to

        WHERE (p.age>=18 AND p.age<30) OR (p.income>=30000 AND p.income<60000)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Recreation'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT i) AS intention,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r1) AS want_to,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to

        WHERE (p.age>60) OR (p.income>=0 AND p.income<30000)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Recreation'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT i) AS intention,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r1) AS want_to,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to

MATCH (p:Person)
        WHERE (p.age>60) OR (p.income>=0 AND p.income<30000)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Recreation'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT i) AS intention,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r1) AS want_to,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to

        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Recreation'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT i) AS intention,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r1) AS want_to,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to
